que escola frequentei:

00:02:55.169 --> 00:02:57.652
"Frequentaste a 
Kennedy School of Government?"

00:02:57.652 --> 00:02:59.418
Eu olho para a pessoa e respondo:

00:02:59.418 --> 00:03:02.418
